sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Mobile App (Client)
    participant Server as Auth Server

    Note over App, Server: Attestation is enabled (required for this request)

    App->>Server: POST /token (header: X-Device-Id)
    Server->>Server: extractAttestationToken(X-Device-Id)

    alt Header missing or empty
        Server-->>App: 400 Bad Request (attestation missing)
    else Header present
        Note over Server: noop accepts any non-empty token
        Server->>Server: add claims attested=true, attestation_level=stub
        Server-->>App: 200 OK (access_token)
    end
